    %center.q-and-a.span6.offset3
      %h3 Quick answers to common questions

      %h4#friends Can I pay for my friends?
      %p Yes! You can choose to pay for yourself or everybody who plays on your server.

      %h4 Will that be expensive if 100 people play on my server?
      %p No! When you pay for your friends, we cap the cost at <span class="highlight">10 people per minute</span>. If you have 100 people playing on your server it costs you the same as 10 people.

      %h4#slots How many people can play on my server?
      %p Unlimited. Minefold's custom built hosting platform dynamically allocates resources to servers. This means that they're lag-free no matter how many of your friends are playing.

